name: Ikigai SR
description:
This model is made to achieve the skin detail seen from my initial model Ikigai 2.5D paired with the Danni 2D lora that's no longer available, without any lora needed!

V2:
Toned back the mix a bit, added in Real Moon. Also integrated a lora I used in Ikigai 2.5D for detail that no longer exists on the site.

My usual settings:
Sampler: DPM++ 2M Karras
Sample Steps: 20-35
Upscaler: ESRGAN_4x
Deniose: 0.5
CFG: 5-9

Model has no integrated VAE. I used Grapefruit VAE for the images above.

By no means is this law, feel free to experiment and I'd love to see your results!!

For inpainting, I generally limit to Only Masked to 800 x 800 or lower and 0.5 denoise (or lower if you want to maintain the initial face look more). It will start to get a little too detailed at higher res'. You shouldn't need to change your prompt at all when inpainting faces to get a good result. This was a goal of mine, as I prefer not to have to do any extra steps in my workflow if possible.

This mix comprises of:
MajicMix Realistic
MIX-Pro-V4
Babes 2.0
FantasticMix

Same as the 2.5D model, this one plays very well with 2D artist style loras!
